Cons: Indicator lights are the top, not the front, so they are not visible from the seating position
After I set up this sound bar using the Audio out 3.5mm jack from my computer to the RCA inputs on this device (cables included), I watched Terminator: Dark Fate. This is only a sound bar so you will not get the full 3D experience because it does not have a subwoofer, but in Theater mode, this is absolutely worth the on-sale price I purchased it at. The room is 15’ x 15’. The surround sound was impressive and the volume is very sufficient (I’m very picky about my sound).</p></div><div class="in-review"><div class="feature-ratings"><h4 class="features-heading">Features</h4><div class="rating-bars"><div class="quality-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Quality</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">5 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled last "> </div></div></div><div class="value-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Value</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">5 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled last "> </div></div></div><div class="ease-of-use-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Ease of Use</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">4 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar  last "> </div></div></div></div></div></div><strong class="v-fw-medium  ugc-recommendation"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="svg-size-s is-recommended-icon" fill="#55555a"><use href="/~assets/bby/_img/int/plsvgdef-frontend/svg/confirm.svg#confirm" xlink:href="/~assets/bby/_img/int/plsvgde