></div></div></div></div><div class="ugc-review-body body-copy-lg"><p class="pre-white-space">I have a TV in the dining area, this is not my main TV, but I was having to turn it up really loud to hear anything.  This sound bar works great in that area.

On one occasion, we started a movie while we were having dinner (a Marvel movie) and the action scene was so loud it caused a lot of distortion, but for everyday news and TV, it works really well.  I use it with an amazon fire stick and it pairs nicely via Bluetooth and optical.  the Fire stick remote also controls the volume, but make sure when powering on the TV, the remote is pointed at the sound bar, or you will have to manually power it on.</p></div><div class="in-review"><div class="feature-ratings"><h4 class="features-heading">Features</h4><div class="rating-bars"><div class="quality-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Quality</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">3 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar   "> </div><div class="rating-bar  last "> </div></div></div><div class="value-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Value</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">5 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled last "> </div></div></div><div class="ease-of-use-rating rating-group"><div class="rating-description">Ease of Use</div><div class="bars-group"><div class="sr-only">4 out of 5</div><div class="rating-bar filled first "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar filled  "> </div><div class="rating-bar  last "> </div></div></div></div></div></div><strong class="v-fw-medium  ugc-recommendation"><svg aria-hidden="true" role="img" viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="svg-size-s is-recommended-icon" fill="#55555a"><use href="/~assets/bby/_img/int/plsvgdef-frontend/svg/confirm.svg#confirm" xlink:href="/~assets/bby/_img/int/plsvgdef-frontend/svg/confirm.svg#confirm"></